## 10. CONCIERGE SYSTEM (TWO FLOWS)

Flow A — Operational (SLA, staff accept/complete):
- Luggage tile → submits to requests table → Concierge dept staff → SLA
- Staff see in active tasks list with accept → complete

Flow B — Reservations (no SLA, manager/staff confirm, guest notified):
- Tours, Car Rental, Taxi, Limo → saved to concierge_bookings table
- Guest books: pickup date/time, return date/time, guests, special requests
- Concierge staff see pending bookings in active tab (Concierge Bookings section)
- Staff can Confirm or Cancel/Reject (with mandatory custom reason message)
- On Confirm → guest gets pop-up notification
- On Cancel → guest gets pop-up notification WITH rejection reason
- Payment at concierge desk (no online payment)

CONCIERGE REJECTION FLOW (Session 4):
- Staff clicks Cancel/Reject → modal opens
- Staff MUST enter reason (button disabled if empty)
- Message saved: "Dear Valued Guest, we regret to inform you that your [service] booking has been cancelled. [Staff reason]. We apologise for any inconvenience..."
- Message shown in guest notification pop-up

