## 21. KNOWN GOTCHAS

1. NEVER use .or('hotel_id.eq.X,hotel_id.is.null') — causes ALL clients to see test data
2. Never strip timezone from timestamps — just .replace(' ','T')
3. useState inside JSX = React hooks crash
4. Unclosed JSX divs = cascading TypeScript errors
5. Always push types.ts WITH App.tsx
6. Multiple JSX siblings in ternary branches need <></> fragment wrapper
7. Logo/cover from restaurants table (r.logo_url) NOT restaurant_settings (s.logo_url)
8. RESTAURANTS constant REMOVED — use restaurants state from DB
9. MENU_ITEMS constant REMOVED — use menuItems state from DB
10. services_config null = all services shown (testing mode)
11. SLA onConflict MUST be 'department,hotel_id' not just 'department'
12. Reservation Agent must use .neq('service_key','room_service') to exclude room service
13. fetchSLA MUST run inside poll interval, not just on mount
14. Concierge cancel modal needs conciergeCancelModal state + conciergeRejectReason state
15. Duplicate icon imports cause TS2300 error — always check before adding imports
16. hotel_clients + super_admin tables must NEVER be deleted (owner data)
17. rejection_reason column added to restaurant_bookings AND concierge_bookings in Session 4

